column1: #FORMAT=WebAnno TSV 3.2
#T_SP=webanno.custom.Referent|entity|infstat
#T_RL=webanno.custom.Coref|type|BT_webanno.custom.Referent
#Text=Would you consider your music to be mathematical ?
#Text=No , not at all .
#Text=It 's completely aesthetic almost .
#Text=It 's about tinkering around with ideas in my head and seeing what kind of sound that actually produces .
#Text=Do you have a favorite mathematician or unsolved mathematical problem ?
#Text=I 'm not that kind of person .
#Text=I liked doing mathematics and learning about it , but I was never into mathematical history beyond what I was working on .
#Text=What 's a trait you deplore in other people ?
#Text=Apathy or laziness .

#Text=I 'm the kind of person who is always doing something and get excited about something , and I find it frustrating when people get good ideas that are interesting and do n't make the most of that .
#Text=Anything I want to do , I 'm all about doing it as much as possible .
#Text=Meanness , selfishness , obviously .
#Text=What ’s a trait you deplore in yourself ?
#Text=It ’s probably twined with my possessiveness and being too controlling of the things I ’m doing , which is probably related to the fact I ’m so excited to do things .
#Text=That ’s the flip side of it , I suppose .
#Text=Even more so , my self-centeredness .
#Text=I spend all my time making this music , and I ’m really proud of it and happy with it , but I kind of feel it is indulging my interests .
#Text=You think that might be a negative ?
#Text=I do , because there are better things I could be doing in this world .
#Text=I do n’t know , I could be more helpful to humanity than just sitting in my room making music , but I enjoy doing it so much that I make the decision to do it .
#Text=That 's a challenge for any human of whether or not to pursue something you think is a greater good or indulge yourself .
#Text=How do you wrestle with that question ?
#Text=I guess like most people I avoid it to a certain degree .
#Text=I hopefully strike some kind of compromise , but very heavy on doing what I ’m excited about .
#Text=Well , we need music in this world and if people are responding to it , you ’re giving something to them .
#Text=Yeah , I hope so , or maybe you are just trying to make me feel good .
#Text=Maybe . [ Laughs ]
#Text=Hillary or Barack ?
#Text=My gut reaction would be Barack , but I ’m not really on top of American politics to endorse either .
#Text=What do you think of Gordon Brown ?
#Text=He 's a funny one to pin down .
#Text=I ca n’t figure him out .
#Text=The effect of having him in government is probably going to be pretty close to the effect of having Tony Blair in government , which is a shame .
#Text=I ’d like to see someone more old Labour and Socialist , I guess .
#Text=There 's always a hint that he is that , but I do n’t think it will be reflected in his policies .
